WITH group_by_parameter as (
    select transaction_columns_groupby as parameter_group
    from MD.CRYPTO_ACQUIRING_DASHBOARD_HELP_TABLE
    where {{transaction_columns_groupby}}
    ),
    main_query as (select CREATED_AT 
                      , TURNOVER_EUR
                      , ID 
                      , REVENUE_EUR
                      , REVENUE_EXCHANGE_EUR
                      , REVENUE_TOPUP_EUR
                      , GMV_EUR
                      , NETWORK_FEE_EUR
                      , FEE_EXCHENGER_EUR
                      , FEE_EUR
                      , Type
                      , MERCHANT_NAME
                      , merchant_type
                      , crypto_currency
                      , fiat_currency
                      , network
      from mart.CRYPTO_ACQUIRING
      where confirmed and {{type}} and {{CREATED_AT}} and {{merchant_name}} and {{merchant_type}} and
          {{crypto_currency}} and {{fiat_currency}}  and {{network}}
          and MERCHANT_NAME not in ('TestMerchantStandart', 'Mercuryo Withdrawal')
      ) 
     
     select 
    date_trunc({{granularity}}, main_query.CREATED_AT) as created_at
    ,     CASE 
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Type'
            THEN main_query.Type
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group  = 'Merchant name'
            THEN main_query.MERCHANT_NAME
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group  = 'Merchant type'
            THEN main_query.merchant_type
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Crypto currency'
            THEN main_query.crypto_currency
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Fiat currency'
            THEN main_query.fiat_currency
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Network'
            THEN main_query.network

        ELSE null end as groupping
    , sum(FEE_EXCHENGER_EUR) as FEE_EXCHENGER_EUR
from main_query 
left join group_by_parameter as groupby
    on 1 = 1
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

WITH 
    main_query as (select CREATED_AT 
                      , TURNOVER_EUR
                      , ID 
                      , REVENUE_EUR
                      , REVENUE_EXCHANGE_EUR
                      , REVENUE_TOPUP_EUR
                      , REVENUE_FEE_EUR
                      , GMV_EUR
                      , FEE_EUR
                      , Type
                      , MERCHANT_NAME
                      , merchant_type
                      , crypto_currency
                      , fiat_currency
      from mart.CRYPTO_ACQUIRING
      where confirmed and {{type}} and {{CREATED_AT}} and {{merchant_name}} and {{merchant_type}} and
          {{crypto_currency}} and {{fiat_currency}}  and {{network}}
          and MERCHANT_NAME not in ('TestMerchantStandart', 'Mercuryo Withdrawal')
      ),
      revenue_fee as (
      select 'REVENUE FEE EUR' as name_revenue
      , REVENUE_FEE_EUR as value_revenue
      , id
      from main_query),
      revenue_topup as (
      select 'REVENUE TOPUP EUR' as name_revenue
      , REVENUE_TOPUP_EUR as value_revenue
      , id
      from main_query),
     revenue_exchange as (
      select 'REVENUE EXCHANGE EUR' as name_revenue
      , REVENUE_EXCHANGE_EUR as value_revenue
      , id
      from main_query),
      all_rev as (select *
      from revenue_fee
      union 
      select *
      from revenue_topup
      union
      select * 
      from revenue_exchange),
      main_table as (
      select name_revenue
      , sum(value_revenue) as value_revenue
      from all_rev
      group by name_revenue)
      
      
      select name_revenue
      , value_revenue
      , value_revenue / sum(value_revenue) over (partition by 1) as percent_revenue
      from main_table
      order by 2 desc

    select transaction_columns_groupby as parameter_group
    from MD.CRYPTO_ACQUIRING_DASHBOARD_HELP_TABLE
    where {{transaction_columns_groupby}}
    ),
    main_query as (select CREATED_AT 
                      , TURNOVER_EUR
                      , ID 
                      , REVENUE_EUR
                      , REVENUE_EXCHANGE_EUR
                      , REVENUE_TOPUP_EUR
                      , GMV_EUR
                      , FEE_EUR
                      , Type
                      , MERCHANT_NAME
                      , merchant_type
                      , crypto_currency
                      , fiat_currency
                      , network
      from mart.CRYPTO_ACQUIRING
      where confirmed and {{type}} and {{CREATED_AT}} and {{merchant_name}} and {{merchant_type}} and
          {{crypto_currency}} and {{fiat_currency}}  and {{network}}
          and MERCHANT_NAME not in ('TestMerchantStandart', 'Mercuryo Withdrawal')
      )
      
      select date_trunc({{granularity}}, CREATED_AT) as dt
    , CASE 
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Type'
            THEN main_query.Type
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group  = 'Merchant name'
            THEN main_query.MERCHANT_NAME
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group  = 'Merchant type'
            THEN main_query.merchant_type
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Crypto currency'
            THEN main_query.crypto_currency
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Fiat currency'
            THEN main_query.fiat_currency
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Network'
            THEN main_query.Network

        ELSE null end as groupping
    , CASE WHEN sum(REVENUE_EUR) != 0
    THEN sum(GMV_EUR)/sum(REVENUE_EUR) end as GMV_2_Revenue
    from main_query 
    left join group_by_parameter as groupby
    on 1 = 1
    group by 1,2

WITH group_by_parameter as (
    select transaction_columns_groupby as parameter_group
    from MD.CRYPTO_ACQUIRING_DASHBOARD_HELP_TABLE
    where {{transaction_columns_groupby}}
    ),
    main_query as (select CREATED_AT

                      , confirmed
                      , Type

                      , crypto_currency
                      , fiat_currency
                      , network
      from mart.CRYPTO_ACQUIRING
      where {{type}} and {{CREATED_AT}} and {{merchant_name}} and {{merchant_type}} and
          {{crypto_currency}} and {{fiat_currency}}  and {{network}}
          and MERCHANT_NAME not in ('TestMerchantStandart', 'Mercuryo Withdrawal')
      ) 
     
     select type
     , CASE 
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Type'
            THEN main_query.Type
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group  = 'Merchant name'
            THEN main_query.MERCHANT_NAME
        WHEN groupby.parameter_group  = 'Merchant type'

    on 1 = 1

        WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Fiat currency'
            THEN main_query.fiat_currency
         WHEN groupby.parameter_group = 'Network'
            THEN main_query.Network

        ELSE null end as groupping
    , sum(NETWORK_FEE_EUR) as NETWORK_FEE_EUR
    from main_query 
    left join group_by_parameter as groupby
    on 1 = 1
    group by 1)
    
    select groupping
    , NETWORK_FEE_EUR
    , NETWORK_FEE_EUR / sum(NETWORK_FEE_EUR) over (partition by 1) as percent_turnover
    from count_gr
    where NETWORK_FEE_EUR > 0
    order by 2 desc

[\"name\",\"PERCENT_TURNOVER\"].column_title: Percent from all Network fee EUR
